<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.8.2">
<l>emmā ṉēyeṉ veḷḷai mūrtti yeṉṉai yāḷvāṉē</l>
<l>yemmā vuruvum vēṇṭu māṟṟā lāvā yeḻilēṟē</l>
<l>cemmā kamalañ ceḻunīr micaikkaṇmalarun tirukkuṭantai</l>
<l>yammā malarkkaṇ vaḷarkiṉ ṟāṉēyeṉnāṉ ceykēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our lord, my white form, o the one who rules me,</l>
<l>You become any great form the way you wish, o graceful bull.</l>
<l>O the one who sleeps with pretty dark flower eyes in Tirukuṭantai</l>
<l>Where eyes of the big red lotus bloom on the rich water, what shall I do?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
